OL,3,CPeers to debate proposed law to ban
OL,4,Cconversion therapy
OL,6,FA proposed law to ban sexual
OL,7,Forientation and gender identity
OL,8,Fconversion practices will be
OL,9,Fconsidered in Parliament on Friday.
OL,11,FIt would become an offence for any
OL,12,Fperson to practise, or to offer to
OL,13,Fpractise, conversion therapy in the UK
OL,14,Funder the Conversion Therapy
OL,15,FProhibition Bill.
OL,17,FLiberal Democrat Baroness Burt of
OL,18,FSolihull has tabled the Bill in a bid
OL,19,Fto press ahead with implementing a ban
OL,20,Fafter Government efforts stalled.
