OL,3,CPeers to debate proposed law to ban
OL,4,Cconversion therapy
OL,6,FConversion therapy practices seek to
OL,7,Fchange or suppress someone's sexual
OL,8,Forientation or gender identity.
OL,10,FThe Government first announced its
OL,11,Fintention to ban so-called "gay cure"
OL,12,Fconversion therapies in 2018 as part
OL,13,Fof its LGBT (lesbian, gay, bisexual
OL,14,Fand transgender) action plan.
OL,16,FThe proposals were initially intended
OL,17,Fto be "universal" and protect all LGBT
OL,18,Fpeople, although in 2022 then-prime
OL,19,Fminister Boris Johnson defended a
OL,20,Fdecision not to include trans people.
