OL,6,FIn January 2023, the Government said
OL,7,Fit would set out how it would ban
OL,8,Fconversion therapy for "everyone" `
OL,9,Fincluding transgender people ` in
OL,10,FEngland and Wales.
OL,12,FEqualities minister Kemi Badenoch, in
OL,13,FDecember 2023, told MPs that she
OL,14,Fremains "determined" to meet the
OL,15,Fpledge to publish a draft Conversion
OL,16,FPractices Bill for pre-legislative
OL,17,Fscrutiny.
