OL,3,CPeers to debate proposed law to ban
OL,4,Cconversion therapy
OL,6,FLady Burt said: "Conversion practices
OL,7,Fdo profound harm to LGBT+ people. The
OL,8,Ffact that the Government cannot even
OL,9,Fcommit to a timeline on delivering a
OL,10,Fban is shameful.
OL,12,F"This issue is too important to let
OL,13,Fthe Conservatives kick the can down
OL,14,Fthe road any longer. I am calling for
OL,15,F(education minister) Baroness Barran
OL,16,Fand her Government to fully commit to
OL,17,Fending this abhorrent practice."
