OL,6,FLady Burt, in the House of Lords
OL,7,Fbriefing for the Bill, also said: "Of
OL,8,Fcourse, it's important to
OL,9,Fdifferentiate between psychological
OL,10,Fpractice or religious advice and
OL,11,Fconversion therapy.
OL,13,F"A therapist, for example, who is
OL,14,Fexploring gender dysphoria with a
OL,15,Fyoung person in good faith ` with no
OL,16,Fpredetermined goal to change how that
OL,17,Fyoung person ought to be ` shouldn't
OL,18,Fbe penalised.
